      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good starting point, but it's a bit generic. To really tailor the marketing campaign, I need more specifics on the actual demographics. Can you get more granular? I'm thinking about things like age, nationality, ethnicity, and specific geographic locations where they'd likely live or vacation. Give me a much more detailed breakdown of who this person actually is.",
