    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. So you're saying the \"core\" demographic is basically just the traditional Western elite? I'm curious though, with how much the wealth landscape is changing globally, wouldn't there be other significant profiles? Like, if we wanted to expand our reach, what would a high-net-worth persona look like in, say, Singapore or Dubai? Or even someone from a different ethnic or cultural background than the European/North American one you mentioned? How would their lifestyle and \"luxury\" values differ from the ones you just described?",
